OL,3,CFresh appeal for information 30 years
OL,4,Cafter Lindsay Rimer murder
OL,6,FThe family of a teenage girl from West
OL,7,FYorkshire who disappeared after she
OL,8,Fwent out to buy a box of cornflakes
OL,9,Fhave pleaded for information to
OL,10,Ffinally bring her killer to justice
OL,11,Fafter 30 years.
OL,13,FLindsay Rimer was just 13 when she
OL,14,Fvanished in Hebden Bridge in 1994. Her
OL,15,Fbody was found in the Rochdale Canal a
OL,16,Ffew months later - she had been
OL,17,Fmurdered, and her body weighed down
OL,18,Fwith a heavy stone.
