OL,3,CFresh appeal for information 30 years
OL,4,Cafter Lindsay Rimer murder
OL,6,FLindsay was last captured on CCTV at
OL,7,Fthe Spar shop in Hebden Bridge on the
OL,8,Fnight of November 7, 1994. Her
OL,9,Fdisappearance triggered a huge police
OL,10,Finvestigation. Officers spoke to more
OL,11,Fthan 5,000 people and examined more
OL,12,Fthan 1,200 vehicles.
OL,14,FOver the decades, there have been a
OL,15,Fnumber of arrests, but no one has even
OL,16,Fbeen charged in connection with
OL,17,FLindsay's murder.
