OL,3,CFresh appeal for information 30 years
OL,4,Cafter Lindsay Rimer murder
OL,6,FNow, as the 30th anniversary of her
OL,7,Fdisappearance approaches, her family,
OL,8,Ffriends and well-wishers have gathered
OL,9,Fin Hebden Bridge as a show of support
OL,10,Fand to launch a new appeal for
OL,11,Finformation.
OL,13,FHer sister Kate, now 50, said:"We're
OL,14,Faiming this appeal at anyone who knows
OL,15,Fanything about what happened to
OL,16,FLindsay. We want that person to come
OL,17,Fforward with whatever information they
OL,18,Fhave which will lead to arresting
OL,19,Fsomeone for the murder of my sister."
