OL,3,CFresh appeal for information 30 years
OL,4,Cafter Lindsay Rimer murder
OL,6,FLindsay's younger sister Juliet, 31,
OL,7,Fwas just a baby at the time of her
OL,8,Fdisappearance.
OL,10,FShe said: "There's someone who knows
OL,11,Fsomething out there that could be the
OL,12,Fmissing piece of information. It might
OL,13,Fbe that they haven't had the
OL,14,Fconfidence to come forward yet. Maybe
OL,15,Fnow is the time to do that."
